Package: scAgentKit
Type: Package
Title: Agent-Friendly Toolkit for Single-Cell RNA-seq Analysis
Version: 0.1.22
Authors@R: person("Kan", "Author", email = "kan@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Atomic, composable functions for single-cell RNA-seq pipelines
    (QC, normalization, integration, clustering, annotation), designed as the
    tool layer of an LLM agent. Every function takes and returns an
    AgentSeurat S4 object that accumulates decision logs and reproducible
    R script snippets, enabling both agent orchestration and publication-grade
    reproducibility.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
